What you need to know:  The “Club” Games are due for July 28 to August 8 in Birmingham while the continental youth games have been programmed tentatively from August 29 to September 9 in the Egyptian capitalKenya Amateur Weightlifting Association Secretary General John Ogolla has been appointed at the Chef de Mission for Team Kenya to the Commonwealth Games while Olympic 5,000m silver medallist Hellen Obiri will be the Chef de Mission for team Kenya for the Africa Youth GamesRugby legend Humphrey Kayange was appointed the Chief Executive Officer and Secretary for Birmingham 2022 Commonwealth Games